data.description: Turnkey investment 2 flat or call this beauty home while collecting rental income from the 2nd unit. Fully renovated and modernized Brick 2 Flat. Each unit features 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. Completely rebuilt from the walls in, this property has it ALL.   No deferred maintenance or Capex needed. Investors Dream.          Brand new kitchen features white shaker cabinets and white Carrera counter top. New bathrooms throughout. NEW Roof, New Garage, New HVAC with air conditioning, NEW plumbing, NEW electric NEW water heaters. NEW windows and doors complimented with refinished hardwood floors. Absolutely turnkey investment or move in ready for a very special home. Clean and dry unfinished basement ready for expansion if needed.   2 Car Garage.   2 units are fully rented so it can be a quality armchair investment from day 1.  Rent is currently $1600 for both units. Tenants pay all utilities.   1 unit can be vacant if needed for an owner occupant.  Low Taxes !!
